sub_title: Bachelor student Erasmus University Rotterdam I ELS Marketing Officer
summary:
I am a second-year student at Erasmus University Rotterdam, pursuing a bachelor's degree in BSc Management of International Social Challenges. 
As of now, I am searching for an internship with an international focus, from September for 2 months


Aside from my studies, I am on the board of Erasmus Language Sharing, as Marketing Officer, where I organise advertisements and events for our team. I also teach beginners level Swedish and all levels of French to students of the university.
